parameters:
Come closer to the livestock fence! The pigs will come
crawling... Isn't it fun?

That knocking sound... Laura? Such a nice sound... More...
Please, more...

Ahh...! Amazing...!! I feel like I'm about to lose
control...!
Ahh... wait...! I can't... handle this... anymore...!!!
S-Stop... Laura...!! I-I'm really... going crazy...!!!

\SE[2]They call this phonophilia. \!\SE[10]This person
always ends up like this. No one has ever seen their face.

Welcome to Hatayaki Village!... That's what it says. Since
there are no tourists, no one will read it.

Ah... Laura-chan, hello...! Um, it's sudden, but do you have
a boyfriend or anything, Laura-chan...?

\SE[3]Boyfriend... well, I don't have one in particular.
\SE[3]Why are you suddenly asking me that?

Ah... I see... Huh...! Well, the thing is, I've been
thinking about confessing to someone I like...

\SE[5]Eh! Is that true!? \SE[21]I'm sure your feelings will
reach them! \SE[14]I'll be cheering for you too!

I hear some noises coming from inside the warehouse...
Should I go inside and investigate?
Here is 'Fun Pigs'! Let's touch the warmth and become happy!

I am growing Prism Herbs for pig farming. Stealing is a
crime. You should never do it. Don't you think it's pitiful
to see cute pigs go hungry?

\SE[15]I am a traveling merchant. \!\SE[15]I came here with
a sense of traveling, but it's such a peaceful and nice
place.

\SE[2]Oh my...! Do you need something? \SE[16]Even if you're
just here to chat, you're welcome!
\SE[15]Well then, please take care and have a safe journey!

\SE[32]The delay will be about a week... I wonder. \SE[38]I
wonder how much I can do on my own...

\SM[double]\SE[10]Oh, welcome back! It seems like you were
able to successfully accomplish your objective! \SE[10]You
have such a nice expression on your face!
\SM[pop]\SE[15]Well then, it's time for Cat's Shop!

\SE[2]Oh my...! Do you need something? \SE[16]Even if you're
just here to chat, you're welcome!

Oh, Laura-chan! If you're going outside, why don't you come
and sit by the bonfire? It will calm your heart and fully
restore your stamina!

Bonfires are the best, aren't they... When I grow up, I'm
going to become a skilled 'Bonfire Artisan' myself!

Hatayaki Village.... A modest yet lively village located in
the outskirts....

\SE[2]Oh, are you going out? \SE[15]It's dangerous for a
girl to go out alone. Why not equip yourself with my
merchandise? (It's not free though!)

\SE[2]Equipment...? But, I'm just going to the back of the
mountain for a bit...

\SE[14]That's exactly why... It's true! Recently, even in
the city, it's become popular for girls to arm themselves!
\SM[double]\SE[25]You're cute, so you can become all cool
and stylish! \SM[rock]\SE[36]Even that special someone will
be head over heels for you...!

\SE[106]Equipping myself as a girl... even that special
someone... \SE[19]Becoming cool and...
\SE[106]captivating...!? \SM[nod]\SE[102]W-Wait, can you
show me...!?

\SM[pop]\SE[15]Welcome! It's time for the Cat Shop!
\SM[nod]\SE[14]Even just browsing is welcome!

\SE[5]Wow! There are so many things! \SM[rock]\SE[28]I might
get overwhelmed...

\SM[nod]\SE[15]At first, it might be a good idea to have a
stock of recovery items and gradually equip yourself with
armor. Who knows? \SM[nod]\SE[15]After all, your life is the
most important thing.

\SE[3]Because I don't know how long this place will remain
peaceful.

\SE[16]I didn't say anything, you know~. \SE[0]Well then,
please take care on your way. If you need anything, feel
free to ask~. \SM[nod]\SE[10]You'll be all cool and
captivating... Big sis!

\SE[16]Thank you very much for your kindness. \SE[16]Stylish
